{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XS79nkNifxrUtaXtibw8NE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The fix is clean and correct. Here's a summary of what was wrong and what I changed:\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL uses `run` as the config key for script steps (e.g., `run = \"go test ./... 2>&1\"`), but both the backend and frontend were looking for `command`/`script` instead.\n\n**Backend fix** (`handler.go:1184-1193`): Changed `step.Config[\"command\"]` and `step.Config[\"script\"]` lookups to `step.Config[\"run\"]`. For inline commands (not file references), `resolveStepContent` will fail to read them as files, and the handler falls back to returning the raw string.\n\n**Frontend fix** (`project_detail.html:263`): Changed the config display filter from `'command'`/`'script'` to `'run'` so that script step commands are shown in the drawer metadata.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":728,"cache_read_input_tokens":51925,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":728},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"70a35ebf-0d6a-46df-8db4-c99ca8eb221c","uuid":"394006ab-79e2-4910-85d9-94333a4e4e26"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":310888,"duration_api_ms":308301,"num_turns":24,"result":"The fix is clean and correct. Here's a summary of what was wrong and what I changed:\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL uses `run` as the config key for script steps (e.g., `run = \"go test ./... 2>&1\"`), but both the backend and frontend were looking for `command`/`script` instead.\n\n**Backend fix** (`handler.go:1184-1193`): Changed `step.Config[\"command\"]` and `step.Config[\"script\"]` lookups to `step.Config[\"run\"]`. For inline commands (not file references), `resolveStepContent` will fail to read them as files, and the handler falls back to returning the raw string.\n\n**Frontend fix** (`project_detail.html:263`): Changed the config display filter from `'command'`/`'script'` to `'run'` so that script step commands are shown in the drawer metadata.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"70a35ebf-0d6a-46df-8db4-c99ca8eb221c","total_cost_usd":1.0047179,"usage":{"input_tokens":18,"cache_creation_input_tokens":43396,"cache_read_input_tokens":507653,"output_tokens":15560,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":43396,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":18,"outputTokens":15560,"cacheReadInputTokens":507653,"cacheCreationInputTokens":43396,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.9141414999999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":45,"outputTokens":2524,"cacheReadInputTokens":229514,"cacheCreationInputTokens":43968,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.0905764,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"ccb0b5fc-d9f1-4561-8f61-651a6021f298"}
